PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 2004-754 which adds military service at Skopje, in the former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia, in direct support of OPERATION ALLIED FORCE, to the list of operations where worthy service may be recognized by the awarding of a Bar to the General Service Medal.
